những thứ cần cài cho vs code

+ C# Dev Kit hoặc C# (chọn 1 trong 2)
+ .NET Extension Pack
+ .NET Install Tool
+ NuGet Gallery
+ C# extension


-- cài các Framework 
+ EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer 8.0.0
+ EntityFrameworkCore.Tools 8.0.0
+ EntityFrameworkCore.Design by Microsoft 8.0.0


-- Chạy code first
dotnet tool install --global dotnet-ef
dotnet build
dotnet ef migrations add init
dotnet ef database update


-- Chạy database first
dotnet tool install --global dotnet-ef
dotnet build
dotnet ef dbcontext scaffold "Your-Connection-String" Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer --output-dir Models
